### FEMEE API - Arquivo de Testes HTTP
### Use este arquivo para testar os endpoints da API
### Configure a variável @token após fazer login

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5299/api
@token = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### =============================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### =============================================

### Health Check básico
GET http://localhost:5299/health
Accept: application/json

### Health Check detalhado
GET http://localhost:5299/health/detailed
Accept: application/json

### Liveness check
GET http://localhost:5299/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Readiness check
GET http://localhost:5299/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### =============================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### =============================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@femee.com",
    "senha": "Admin@123"
}

### Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Novo Usuario",
    "email": "novo@femee.com",
    "senha": "Senha@123",
    "tipoUsuario": 3
}

### =============================================
### USUÁRIOS
### =============================================

### Listar todos os usuários (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Buscar usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### =============================================
### TIMES
### =============================================

### Listar todos os times
GET {{baseUrl}}/times
Accept: application/json

### Buscar time por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/times/1
Accept: application/json

### Buscar time por slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/times/slug/meu-time
Accept: application/json

### Criar time (Admin/Capitao)
POST {{baseUrl}}/times
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Novo Time",
    "slug": "novo-time",
    "descricao": "Descrição do time",
    "logoUrl": "https://example.com/logo.png",
    "capitaoId": 1
}

### =============================================
### CAMPEONATOS
### =============================================

### Listar todos os campeonatos
GET {{baseUrl}}/campeonatos
Accept: application/json

### Buscar campeonato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/campeonatos/1
Accept: application/json

### Campeonatos por status (0=Planejado, 1=Inscricoes, 2=EmAndamento, 3=Finalizado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/campeonatos/status/1
Accept: application/json

### Criar campeonato (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/campeonatos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "titulo": "Campeonato de Verão 2026",
    "descricao": "Grande campeonato de CS2",
    "jogoId": 1,
    "dataInicio": "2026-03-01T00:00:00",
    "dataFim": "2026-03-30T00:00:00",
    "premiacao": 10000.00,
    "limiteParticipantes": 16
}

